{"tid":2223974,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"《暗黑破壞神Diablo 4》確定採用開放世界 過場動畫呈現自訂裝甲","createTime":"2020-09-30T08:01:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-02T11:40:53.000Z","uid":25345,"like":5,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"96a5554f9d8a88ea8d33edd1925bddcebcdd667e","tid":2223974,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T08:01:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200630/354671555416035328.jpeg/3KA806QYf-Pm-K9FK2t0Je1JkWgGudru-b9NTPm_TUw?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200630%2F354671555416035328.jpeg%2F3KA806QYf-Pm-K9FK2t0Je1JkWgGudru-b9NTPm_TUw%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=f15ccee4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBlizzard 近日揭露開發中動作角色扮演遊戲新作《暗黑破壞神 4》季度進度報告，讓玩家得知最新開發狀況，並分享開發中遊戲截圖。<br />\n<br />\n關於敘事表現上，本作將採用即時運算過場動畫，讓玩家為了冒險而選擇的裝甲也能呈現在劇情故事中，且讓關卡與劇情畫面無縫接軌。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/cis/5e292ba8e8996929d68e0616.jpg/uUyJdy6_owChFQe9NwcGl56Nt9yB75tHUfCWWVHwllk?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fcis%2F5e292ba8e8996929d68e0616.jpg%2FuUyJdy6_owChFQe9NwcGl56Nt9yB75tHUfCWWVHwllk%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=07220468&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/cis/5e292ba9f109dd29dc575f10.jpg/cl6gpL6NXnjJdFOJfxid-Qvorxtl3Iic8XyKaPF8img?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fcis%2F5e292ba9f109dd29dc575f10.jpg%2Fcl6gpL6NXnjJdFOJfxid-Qvorxtl3Iic8XyKaPF8img%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=556334d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本作確定採用開放世界世界設計，直衝主線可以花費全數內容的一半時間完成，而且支線也可以在主線通關後回來重玩。以目前開放的「大乾原」擁有許多事件、世界 PVP、以及敵人營地。但玩家奪回區域時都會看到地貌世界的變化。探索這個世界還能準備座騎進行移動。<br />\n<br />\n多人遊戲元素上，關鍵劇情只有單人表現，城鎮可以遇到路人，直到世界頭目可以看到更多玩家一起參與，地城組隊內才有隊友呈現。開發團隊也坦言《暗黑破壞神 4》現階段開發連 alpha、beta 程度都還不算，但由於停辦 Blizzcon 開發團隊以此方式與玩家分享開發進度，觀察玩家對什麼主題最有興趣，後續揭露更多資訊"},{"pid":"19418679abfdfccbe5ebb1409023a92bb4b81e68","tid":2223974,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T08:47:32.000Z","msg":"大波羅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"558c7300ee00c8aa3a893168d1da69b48580fb76","tid":2223974,"uid":78353,"like":42,"dislike":2,"score":40,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T08:54:44.000Z","msg":"共雪，不了"},{"pid":"75d908c486ead332605c4944aeea02fa7b81282e","tid":2223974,"uid":25345,"like":15,"dislike":25,"score":-10,"quote":{"pid":"558c7300ee00c8aa3a893168d1da69b48580fb76","tid":2223974,"uid":78353,"like":42,"dislike":2,"score":40,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T08:54:44.000Z","msg":"共雪，不了"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T09:02:51.000Z","msg":"最後咪一樣爆買<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3818d51ac3065243cf24837305d8717c6cae824d","tid":2223974,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T09:10:11.000Z","msg":"Diablo 4：Guild Wars？<br />\n定係Diablo 4：RIFT？"},{"pid":"5528b4d555b51f972a9f6e639fe66eb1b5f12777","tid":2223974,"uid":152500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T09:13:24.000Z","msg":"有撚派先出啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7ca51b24789cd1d06ba3e706607284d9dc6527b","tid":2223974,"uid":110832,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T09:14:58.000Z","msg":"開發團隊也坦言《暗黑破壞神 4》現階段開發連 alpha、beta 程度都還不算<br />\n<br />\n共雪"},{"pid":"46d41239b17fe4b6d44e4137c809f11266b750ce","tid":2223974,"uid":144024,"like":9,"dislike":5,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T09:41:05.000Z","msg":"先唔理佢共唔共雪，以前SC/ Diablo / WC 真係正到爆<br />\n但係Warcraft 3/ WOW 之後真係一隻不如一隻<br />\n<br />\nSC2無乜新意，不過都叫收貨啦<br />\nDiablo 3 夠膽死出隻半製成品出黎，有開始仲加埋真錢拍賣場，食相核突到呢。。。<br />\n係，我知D3喺無數patch 之後一樣好好玩，之不過已經令大量玩家流失。<br />\n<br />\n最過份係隻WC3 remake 。<br />\n屌佢老味出beta嗰陣已經全世界屌鬼，delay 2個月執屎都預撚咗仲會有問題，算，我打WC3打咗大大話話6-7年，出remake 一樣訂咗，預咗等佢patch 。<br />\n<br />\n只不過。。。一出嗰陣各類bug嘅出現，入到game 唔彈game 都frame rate 跌到個位數。兵嘅動作生硬，server 又平均成2-300 ping。打story mode 啲過場動畫呢？blizz con嗰陣話重製動畫，更細緻更靚更生動，結果？仲閪過原版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nWc3最好玩係對戰，但一出嗰陣無ladder ranking ，連custom game都比佢搞閪埋。呢隻係我中過最伏唧 game，沒有之一。搞一大輪得舊屎，倒不如一開始唔開發直接relaunch 引新人玩好過啦<br />\n<br />\n到而家仲埋奶共？"},{"pid":"e80db5b75550c9b43f9a1b6e2293617d1c87345f","tid":2223974,"uid":111253,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T10:16:27.000Z","msg":"D3初頭真錢拍賣甩到手果班人真係賺到笑"},{"pid":"7418f40ed942c43d1d6bd79f94e31b4bb1603496","tid":2223974,"uid":259520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T10:24:53.000Z","msg":"有無講可以同時幾多人玩??<br />\n<br />\n之前D pvp系統幾失敗下."},{"pid":"b6d0b3ccf1514a667b31cd4b476c28a02ade7f9c","tid":2223974,"uid":11858,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"7418f40ed942c43d1d6bd79f94e31b4bb1603496","tid":2223974,"uid":259520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T10:24:53.000Z","msg":"有無講可以同時幾多人玩??<br />\n<br />\n之前D pvp系統幾失敗下."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T10:27:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fde252d4d4d910427b50c1d2326a6bac6e0960d9","tid":2223974,"uid":172889,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7418f40ed942c43d1d6bd79f94e31b4bb1603496","tid":2223974,"uid":259520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T10:24:53.000Z","msg":"有無講可以同時幾多人玩??<br />\n<br />\n之前D pvp系統幾失敗下."},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T10:37:12.000Z","msg":"兄弟，你一定未玩過d2 hardcore pvp"},{"pid":"b5a55cbf7c9a480ce31d8db6486b31c1d13345c7","tid":2223974,"uid":327462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T10:40:18.000Z","msg":"叫支那狗買埋我嗰份<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a1d7e5695348e46a4467cbc55adc4a38df56aed","tid":2223974,"uid":188310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply